{"tid":1053971,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"自大撚收皮啦","createTime":"2019-03-09T13:16:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-19T14:15:13.000Z","uid":161743,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e66c4246b723bedc43e0c0e4e351f31e754a3edc","tid":1053971,"uid":161743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T13:16:17.000Z","msg":"有個舊同學一年1,2次中學同學眾會都會見<br />\n以前中學都冇乜嘢嘅 定可能未表現出嚟啦 到依家出嚟做嘢就覺得佢好撚煩膠<br />\n佢份人冇家底冇樣 學歷普通啦 借full grant讀u水泡科<br />\n次次出嚟都問舊同學人工 伴侶經濟能力(關你撚事咩) 然後暗自比較 覺得自己先係最好 <br />\n又話自己冇父幹又乜乜柒柒 勁嫉妒啲有父幹嘅朋友 成日係背後講佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又話成日係u都有人抄佢牌 <br />\n下你喎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 老作咋話定盲撚咗呀啲厹 當你冇老作 香港呀豬呀狗都女神架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係唔洗重覆咁撚多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實呢個世界有樣有學歷有家境嘅人真係好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出親嚟不斷曬命 真係越自卑嘅人越自大<br />\n好撚憎啲自大撚 人外有人天外有天 咪撚活係自己個世界啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9d76b4976c839469867a3e64dbab7089a05d73e","tid":1053971,"uid":201604,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T13:16:50.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"5ebb2777f49f6da96a5709f9f4af080d6be4f16a","tid":1053971,"uid":38904,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T13:18:19.000Z","msg":"啲女人俾人抄咗一次牌就成日攞住嚟講架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a030e9c2e3692fa508aa66508c69ab27fb0b9133","tid":1053971,"uid":161743,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5ebb2777f49f6da96a5709f9f4af080d6be4f16a","tid":1053971,"uid":38904,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T13:18:19.000Z","msg":"啲女人俾人抄咗一次牌就成日攞住嚟講架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T13:20:29.000Z","msg":"係每一年聚會都講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講極唔厭 又話係u Libra 有人比紙仔佢<br />\n係ig story又講係u個課室又有人抄佢牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n煩撚到 有時想講下其他話題都唔得"},{"pid":"99557c6caf809d748a1585ef91aadb74d4ea5993","tid":1053971,"uid":215301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T11:43:48.000Z","msg":"通常無料先會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96ceb076af743534366876c83ef01761817dfa7d","tid":1053971,"uid":161195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T12:55:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fe33fd9efcfcfac4248854eded5260c9f7fc576b","tid":1053971,"uid":161743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99557c6caf809d748a1585ef91aadb74d4ea5993","tid":1053971,"uid":215301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T11:43:48.000Z","msg":"通常無料先會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T14:15:13.000Z","msg":"啱呀 井底之蛙到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />越自卑越自大"}]}